// Copy this file to `Local.xcconfig` (same folder) and set your API URL.
// `Local.xcconfig` is gitignored — it is your personal ".env".
// Used by Release builds (TestFlight). The `$()` keeps `//` from being a comment.
//
// Example with an ngrok tunnel pointing at your local NestJS API:
API_BASE_URL = https:/$()/your-subdomain.ngrok-free.app
